<p>This article is about the play by Richard Greenberg. For the album by The Clientele, see <ref target="/wiki/The_Violet_Hour_(album)" title="The Violet Hour (album)">The Violet Hour (album)</ref>.</p>
<p>The Violet Hour is a play by <ref target="/wiki/Richard_Greenberg" title="Richard Greenberg">Richard Greenberg</ref> which premiered at the <ref target="/wiki/South_Coast_Repertory" title="South Coast Repertory">South Coast Repertory</ref> in 2002 and ran on <ref target="/wiki/Broadway_theatre" title="Broadway theatre">Broadway</ref> in 2003.</p>

